## Protobuf Kullanımı
```protobuf
// message.proto
syntax = "proto3";
message Person {
  string name = 1;
  int32 age = 2;
  repeated string emails = 3;
}
```
```bash
protoc --python_out=. message.proto
```
```python
from message_pb2 import Person
p = Person(name='Ali', age=30)
bytes_data = p.SerializeToString()
p2 = Person.FromString(bytes_data)
```
